  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 425°F/ Gas 7</p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>sweet potato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> (skins on) into small, bite-sized pieces</p>\n<p>Trim the green stalks off the <strong>aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and chop into bite-sized pieces</p>\n<p>Deseed the <strong>red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-chilli-yoghurt/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped vegetables</strong> to a baking tray with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[5 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>cumin seeds</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up </p>\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until everything is cooked through </p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-chilli-yoghurt/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong> finely</p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-chilli-yoghurt/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the <strong>basa fillets</strong> dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p>\n<p>Add 3 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> to a plate with the <strong>ground cumin</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>flour mixture</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-chilli-yoghurt/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>basa fillets</strong> to the plate and press them into the <strong>flour mixture</strong> until fully coated</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-chilli-yoghurt/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated basa fillets</strong>, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 2 min on each side or until cooked through and lightly crisp – this is your<strong> crispy fried fish</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-chilli-yoghurt/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and <strong>Sriracha</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>chilli yoghurt</strong></p>\n<p>Once cooked, mix the<strong> vegetables </strong>with the<strong> chopped spring onion </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> chopped coriander </strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">– these are your<strong> roasted vegetables </strong></span></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-chilli-yoghurt/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>fried fish</strong> over the <strong>roasted vegetables</strong></p>\n<p>Drizzle over the <strong>chilli yoghurt</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining coriander</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
